When the pandemic hit, Australia's Dr. Keith Chappell led a team of researchers in developing a vaccine for Covid-19 (the team’s avg age… 30) The weight of the world was on their shoulders. Watch how they faced an unparalleled crisis in the new @CNN Film #RaceForTheVaccine now.

Dr. Kizzmekia Corbett led the research on the Moderna vaccine. See how her interest in studying coronaviruses gave her team a head start at getting a vaccine to market. Watch the new @CNN Film #RaceForTheVaccine now
